      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Thirteen equals one",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.18,
      "endTime": 10.09
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Was the vicar pleased that the clock was striking? Why?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.1,
      "endTime": 16.62,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Our vicar is always raising money for one cause or another,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 16.63,
      "endTime": 20.86,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but he has never managed to get enough money to have the church clock repaired.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 20.87,
      "endTime": 26.48
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The big clock which used to strike the hours day and night was damaged many years ago and has been silent ever since.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 26.49,
      "endTime": 36.37
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "One night, however, our vicar woke up with a start:the clock was striking the hours!",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 36.38,
      "endTime": 43.47,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Looking at his watch, he saw that it was one o'clock,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 43.48,
      "endTime": 47.37,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "Watch",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "手表"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but the bell struck thirteen times before it stopped.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 47.38,
      "endTime": 51.9,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Armed with a torch, the vicar went up into the clock tower to see what was going on.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 51.91,
      "endTime": 58.02,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In the torchlight, he caught sight of a figure whom he immediately recognized as Bill Wilkins, our local grocer.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 58.03,
      "endTime": 66.23,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'Whatever are you doing up here Bill?' asked the vicar in surprise.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 66.24,
      "endTime": 71.56,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "Here",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "这里"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'I'm trying to repair the bell, ' answered Bill.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 71.57,
      "endTime": 75.22
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'I've been coming up here night after night for weeks now.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 75.23,
      "endTime": 78.63,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Here",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "这里"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "You see, I was hoping to give you a surprise.'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 78.64,
      "endTime": 82.39,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'You certainly did give me a surprise!' said the vicar.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 82.4,
      "endTime": 85.81,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "Me",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "我（宾格）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'You've probably woken up everyone in the village as well.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 85.82,
      "endTime": 89.5,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Still, I'm glad the bell is working again.'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 89.51,
      "endTime": 93,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'That's the trouble, vicar, 'answered Bill. 'It's working all right,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 93.01,
      "endTime": 98.06,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "but I'm afraid that at one o'clock it will strike thirteen times and there's nothing I can do about it.'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 98.07,
      "endTime": 105,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'We'll get used to that, Bill, 'said the vicar.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 105.01,
      "endTime": 108.04,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'Thirteen is not as good as one, but it's better than nothing.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 108.05,
      "endTime": 112.94,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Now let's go downstairs and have a cup of tea.'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 112.95,
      "endTime": 117.95
    }
  ]
